thresholds.prompt:
RunPod balance is now $${balance:.2f}, below the $10 warning threshold. Running pods:
{pods_json}

For each pod, decide: keep running, or terminate? If terminating, run `runpodctl pod delete <id>`. Be conservative — only terminate pods clearly past their useful life. Reply with a one-line summary of what you did.

RunPod balance CRITICAL: $${balance:.2f}, below the $2 threshold. Running pods:
{pods_json}

Terminate any pod that isn't actively producing artifacts. Use `runpodctl pod delete <id>` for each. Aggression > caution at this level.

RunPod EMERGENCY: balance $${balance:.2f}. RunPod kills pods around the $0.10 mark, leaving stranded artifacts that cost $10 to recover. Terminate ALL pods immediately:
{pods_json}
Run `runpodctl pod delete <id>` on every single one. Don't ask, don't pause.
